casebody.data:
NOKIA INC., et al., petitioners,
v.
INTERNATIONAL TRADE COMMISSION, et al. No. 12-1352. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2013. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit denied. The CHIEF JUSTICE and Justice BREYER took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
